<Page x:Class="MarathonSkills2k16.Pages.MarathonInfo"
      xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
      xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml"
      xmlns:mc="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/markup-compatibility/2006" 
      xmlns:d="http://schemas.microsoft.com/expression/blend/2008" 
      xmlns:local="clr-namespace:MarathonSkills2k16.Pages"
      mc:Ignorable="d" 
      d:DesignHeight="960" d:DesignWidth="1280"
      Title="MarathonInfo">

    <Grid>
        <Grid.RowDefinitions>
            <RowDefinition Height="200"/>
            <RowDefinition/>
        </Grid.RowDefinitions>
        <TextBlock Grid.Row="0" FontSize="36" HorizontalAlignment="Center" Margin="0,100,0,0">Информация о Marathon Skills 2016</TextBlock>
        <Grid Grid.Row="1" >
            <Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                <ColumnDefinition/>
                <ColumnDefinition />
            </Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
            <Grid Grid.Column="0">
                <Grid.RowDefinitions>
                    <RowDefinition Height="170"/>
                    <RowDefinition/>
                </Grid.RowDefinitions>
                <Button Grid.Row="0" Width="250" Height="150" BorderThickness="1,1,1,1" Background="#FFE5E5E5" BorderBrush="#FF1F1F1F" VerticalAlignment="Top">
                    <TextBlock FontSize="18" Foreground="#FF5B5B5B" HorizontalAlignment="Center" VerticalAlignment="Center" Width="288" TextWrapping="Wrap" TextAlignment="Center"><Bold FontSize="24" FontWeight="Normal">Карта марафона</Bold><LineBreak/>(Нажмите, чтобы открыть интерактивную карту)</TextBlock>

                </Button>
                <Grid Grid.Row="1" Width="250" Height="150" VerticalAlignment="Top">
                    <Border Width="120" Height="70" BorderThickness="1,1,1,1" Background="#FFE5E5E5" BorderBrush="#FF1F1F1F" VerticalAlignment="Top" HorizontalAlignment="Left">
                        <TextBlock FontSize="18" Foreground="#FF5B5B5B" HorizontalAlignment="Center" VerticalAlignment="Center" Width="288" TextWrapping="Wrap" TextAlignment="Center">Photo</TextBlock>
                    </Border>
                    <Border Width="120" Height="70" BorderThickness="1,1,1,1" Background="#FFE5E5E5" BorderBrush="#FF1F1F1F" VerticalAlignment="Top" HorizontalAlignment="Right">
                        <TextBlock FontSize="18" Foreground="#FF5B5B5B" HorizontalAlignment="Center" VerticalAlignment="Center" Width="288" TextWrapping="Wrap" TextAlignment="Center">Photo</TextBlock>
                    </Border>
                    <Border Width="120" Height="70" BorderThickness="1,1,1,1" Background="#FFE5E5E5" BorderBrush="#FF1F1F1F" VerticalAlignment="Bottom" HorizontalAlignment="Left">
                        <TextBlock FontSize="18" Foreground="#FF5B5B5B" HorizontalAlignment="Center" VerticalAlignment="Center" Width="288" TextWrapping="Wrap" TextAlignment="Center">Photo</TextBlock>
                    </Border>
                    <Border Width="120" Height="70" BorderThickness="1,1,1,1" Background="#FFE5E5E5" BorderBrush="#FF1F1F1F" VerticalAlignment="Bottom" HorizontalAlignment="Right">
                        <TextBlock FontSize="18" Foreground="#FF5B5B5B" HorizontalAlignment="Center" VerticalAlignment="Center" Width="288" TextWrapping="Wrap" TextAlignment="Center">Photo</TextBlock>
                    </Border>
                </Grid>
            </Grid>
            <Grid Grid.Column="1">
                <Grid.RowDefinitions>
                    <RowDefinition Height="100"/>
                    <RowDefinition Height="100"/>
                    <RowDefinition Height="100"/>
                </Grid.RowDefinitions>
                <TextBlock Foreground="#FF727272" FontSize="20" TextWrapping="Wrap" Grid.Row="0"  VerticalAlignment="Top">Информация о навыках марафона 2016 пойдет сюда. Информация может покрыть расположение, время, расстояние, рекордные времена, достопримечательности, и т.д</TextBlock>
                <TextBlock Foreground="#FF727272" FontSize="20" TextWrapping="Wrap" Grid.Row="1" VerticalAlignment="Top">Информация о навыках марафона 2016 пойдет сюда. Информация может покрыть расположение, время, расстояние, рекордные времена, достопримечательности, и т.д</TextBlock>
                <TextBlock Foreground="#FF727272" FontSize="20" TextWrapping="Wrap" Grid.Row="2" VerticalAlignment="Top">Информация о навыках марафона 2016 пойдет сюда. Информация может покрыть расположение, время, расстояние, рекордные времена, достопримечательности, и т.д</TextBlock>
            </Grid>
        </Grid>
    </Grid>
</Page>
